{"id": "1450335135592480851", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "A heads-up:\n\nWith new codes & new mechanisms implemented along with the latest revamps, the game **will fail to parse the number when content in [] brackets is different from the original chinese.**\n\nWe are aware that **previously, volunteers may have changed certain [] and <> bracket tag content for better clarity.**\nWe will now** temporarily revert those changes **so it doesn't fail to parse the numbers.", "timestamp": "2025-12-16T03:54:02.249000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-16T04:01:54.242000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1450335134753493083", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 85804, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1450335134753493083/image.png?ex=6a321a5a&is=6a30c8da&hm=a8aa16decd18c894677a7380399f3800fe72040f49443379ddc7e876e1cab57b&"}, {"id": "1450335135168860293", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 137990, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1450335135168860293/image.png?ex=6a321a5a&is=6a30c8da&hm=915c978375797220da8ae5d3a1f60d608da9e5f1a740717f6067a4fe3a389b98&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
